#
# Goal
# ----
# 1. Attach ACS block‚Äëgroup socioeconomic columns (population, median income,
#    poverty count) to **each** rat sighting (point‚Äëlevel).
# 2. Summarise at the block‚Äëgroup level to get calls + call‚Äërate per 10‚ÄØ000.
# 3. Save both products for Tableau: a point CSV and a BG summary CSV.
#
# Prereqs
# ‚Ä¢ You ran 022_spatial_join.R ‚Üí `output/rats_enriched.geojson` exists.
# ‚Ä¢ You have a Census API key in the env‚Äëvar `CENSUS_API_KEY`.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
